    "name": {
      "_dirName": "name",
      "_dirType": "String",
      "_value": "Luke the Security Guy's Wish to Travel"
    },
    "area": {
      "_dirName": "area",
      "_dirType": "Int",
      "_value": 12
    },
    "0": {
      "_dirName": "0",
      "_dirType": "String",
      "_value": "I hear that #b#p226##k the Security Guy made up his mind on something..."
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "String",
      "_value": "I met #p226# at the entrance of the dungeon again. The Snake Drink from back then is gone now because he and his mom drank it all... Anyway, #p226# said he’s done with the boring life of a security guard and has decided to go on an adventure. To make a glove fit for the journey, #p504# of #m10004000# asked for #b1 #t4031033#, 10 #t4010105#s, 30 #t4000036#s, 20 #t4000050#s, and 20 #t4003000#s#k! I’m guessing he wants me to gather them for him... Oh, and apparently, the fairies of #m10002000# might know something about #t4031033#~"
    },
    "2": {
      "_dirName": "2",
      "_dirType": "String",
      "_value": "I brought #p226# the materials he needed to make the gloves and received the treasured heirloom helmet, #b#t1002165##k, in return. It feels like I got the short end of the deal... but since it’s a family heirloom passed down for generations, I can’t really complain..."
    },
    "demandSummary": {
      "_dirName": "demandSummary",
      "_dirType": "String",
      "_value": "#i4031033# #t4031033# #b#c4031033##k / 1\\n#i4010105# #t4010105# #b#c4010105##k / 10\\n#i4000036# #t4000036# #b#c4000036##k / 30\\n#i4000050# #t4000050# #b#c4000050##k / 20\\n#i4003000# #t4003000# #b#c4003000##k / 20"
    }
  },
