  "Say": {
    "_dirName": "Say",
    "_dirType": "sub",
    "0": {
      "_dirName": "0",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Hey! You're the one that helped me make a tasty Snake Drink for my mom! I'm sorry to say this, but... my mom and I drank it all... hehe... anyway, you look much stronger than before! Maybe you could even surpass me one day... well, that's not going to happen though, hahahah..."
      },
      "1": {
        "_dirName": "1",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Okay, I think you can do it since you've gotten much stronger since then...  I've actually been thinking about going on a journey somewhere... I'm getting tired of being the security guy here... I'm trying to make solid equipment for myself to do that, so I visited #p504# in #m10004000#, and... he wants me to get some RIDICULOUS materials for it!!! Those are so rare to begin with..."
      },
      "2": {
        "_dirName": "2",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "I'm trying to be a warrior, and um... can you get me the materials #p504# asked me to get? I tried, but it's too hard for me... Don't worry, I'll reward you well for your work. What do you think? Isn't it good for both of us?"
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Yes! Actually, I really wanted to make a nice glove... and to make it, I need #b1 #t4031033#, 10 #t4010105#s, 30 #t4000036#s, 20 #t4000050#s and 20 #t4003000#s#k. Oh, the fairies might know about #b#t4031033##k. Alright, I'm counting on you! If you get me the materials, I'll definitely give you something nice in return."
        }
      },
      "no": {
        "_dirName": "no",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "You must be really busy right now. If you ever have spare time, please come back and do me that favor! It's very important to me!"
        }
      }
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Oh my goodness, I can't believe you got everything! Sweet! If I get this to #p504#... wow, it's going to be one incredible glove... Oh yeah, I'll give you something good for doing me a favor. This helmet has been passed down in my family for generations, so please take good care of it."
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "You got the #b#t1002165##k, right? Thanks for your hard work. It'll definitely help you on your journey so use it well! Well then, time to go make these gloves..."
        }
      },
      "stop": {
        "_dirName": "stop",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "sub"
        },
        "item": {
          "_dirName": "item",
          "_dirType": "sub",
          "0": {
            "_dirName": "0",
            "_dirType": "String",
            "_value": "You haven't gotten all the materials needed for the gloves yet? Get me #b1 #t4031033#, 10 #t4010105#s, 30 #t4000036#s, 20 #t4000050#s and 20 #t4003000#s#k! The fairies may know something about #b#t4031033##k. Keep working!"
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
